Mapping from the FBQC version of the fusion complex to
the 3d subsystem code, one simply replaces fusions by qubits,
and maps the support of resource-state stabilizers and check
operators to these qubits appropriately: resource state stabi-
lizers correspond to gauge generators and checks of the fu-
sion network correspond to stabilizers of the subsystem code.
